app_name: Groups Treatment Groups Apple Translate Realtime Translate Translator
app_description: The perfect translation and dictionary application for camera and voice translation in more than 100 languages. Turn your phone into a real time translation device. Choose two languages and communicate easily anywhere in the world. Language is no longer an obstacle! Main feature: Translation in more than 100 languages. Conversation translator voice to voice dialogue. Camera translator for menu or logo. Website translator translate website in Safari. AR Translator translate in Augmented Reality. Keyboard Translator for Messaging. Voice Translator for Apple Watch. Share Translator for copying and share. App Shortcuts use Siri and Spotlight to run translator. Family Sharing share subscriptions with your family. Information about auto renewal: Subscription will automatically renew unless auto renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Subscriptions can be managed by the user and automatic renewal can be turned off by going to the user s Account Settings after purchase. When a user purchases a subscription any unused portion during the free trial period will be confiscated. Payment will be deducted from the iTunes account when confirming the purchase. Account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours before the end of the current period. The cost depends on the plan selected.
